detailedRequirements:
Competition Task Overview

We have a website prototype with many html files, when we tried to deploy it to a server the server complained the file names are too long.

The purpose of this F2F is to update the file names so they are short enough and can be deployed without errors, we need you to shorten the file names and update all references in the links.

Technology Overview
HTML
finalSubmissionGuidelines:
Submission Deliverables

A single zip file with all the updated files.

Final Submission

For each member, the final submission should be uploaded via the challenge detail page on topcoder.com.
